4. life cycle rules in s3
Ans:- S3 lifecycle rules are used to automatically manage objects during their lifetime by transitioning them between storage classes or expiring them, based on predefined conditions.
5. What are the storage class
Ans:- S3 storage classes define how data is stored, accessed, and priced, based on access frequency, latency needs, and durability requirements.
